  m_text: 'There is a strange bookshelf in the library. One book looks different
    from the others. It is an old fairy tale book. Maybe the secret passage is hidden
    behind this shelf.

    Listen to the story and write down the numbers you hear.

    IMPORTANT:
    Write the numbers in the correct order and leave ONE SPACE after each number.
    Example: 10 20 30'
